(4345,599,"location_description","Texas’ Capital Austin lies at the edge of the famed Texas Hill Country. The Austin metropolitan area is one of the fastest growing communities in the United States, ranking now as the 14th largest city in the country. Austin has developed a thriving technology sector and has become a leading center of technology in Texas and the Southwest, earning the nickname “Silicon Hills”.\r\nCCN’s Austin office is a further extension of the firm’s growth in the state of Texas, providing a platform for serving Austin-based companies doing business in Mexico, as well as international businesspeople and investors locating to Austin. The CCN Austin office is led by firm founding partner Rene Cacheaux."),
