(4411,608,"location_description","The City of Querétaro is located approximately two hours north of Mexico City and offers many attractive options for investment and development. More than 600 international companies have established operations in the State of Queretaro. Queretaro forms the anchor of Mexico’s new aeronautics industry and features high quality industrial parts and immediate access to rail, highway and energy infrastructure.\r\n\r\nQueretaro is the home of CCN’s Corporate Center, where the firm’s attorneys maintain the corporate records and books of our clients’ Mexican entities. Further, attorneys in CCN’s Querétaro office have the capacity to work on a wide array of matters, including those in the corporate, labor, administrative, intellectual property, litigation, real estate and automotive areas."),
