(11971,1084,"location_description","The City Reynosa is in the heart of the Burgos Basin and with immediate access to the Interstate-69 corridor, it is the home of 14 industrial parks, hosting U.S. and other foreign companies doing business in Mexico.\r\n\r\nThe city of Reynosa is distinguished by its economic vitality and location on the border as a sister city of McAllen, Texas. It serves a strategic point of international trade and is a hub for the manufacturing and energy industries.\r\n\r\nWorking in conjunction with the firm’s McAllen office, attorneys in CCN’s Reynosa location serve clients in the region on real estate, energy, manufacturing, immigration, labor and litigation matters."),
